Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.82,0:01:43.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我站住！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.27,0:01:46.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空易拉罐要扔进垃圾箱！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.86,0:01:48.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.23,0:01:50.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空易拉罐要扔进垃圾箱！
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(title)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.80,0:01:55.80,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傘不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.63,0:02:01.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请留步
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.35,0:02:08.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是可疑人物
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.38,0:02:10.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轨道用于通行
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.15,0:02:12.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,规则用来遵守
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.38,0:02:12.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs32}注：轨道（レール）和规则（ルール）在日语中发音相近
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.23,0:02:15.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人称弗拉明戈武士就是我！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.90,0:02:23.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以乱丢垃圾
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.50,0:02:25.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？但是这里可是垃圾场啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.07,0:02:31.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}垃圾和可回收垃圾的分类及回收日
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.07,0:02:31.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs32}咨询电话…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.07,0:02:31.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs40}可燃垃圾 周五、二
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.07,0:02:31.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs40}不可燃垃圾 周四
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.07,0:02:31.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs40}可回收垃圾 周三
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.07,0:02:31.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs40}塑料垃圾 周一
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.07,0:02:31.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs40}大型垃圾 每月第2个星期一
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.07,0:02:31.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs40}*请务必遵守
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.16,0:02:33.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在还没到周五！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.45,0:02:36.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你太斤斤计较了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.43,0:02:40.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…不 规定就是这样写的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.08,0:02:43.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那小哥你能帮我扔垃圾吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.85,0:02:46.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我早上起不来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.71,0:02:47.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.67,0:02:48.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等 等一下！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.26,0:02:55.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 第二天早上
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.47,0:02:58.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那袋垃圾就被放在了我家门前
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.85,0:03:00.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您觉得是那位小哥放的？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.81,0:03:04.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回头想想 那小哥搞不好是个变态
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.48,0:03:05.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扮得怪里怪气的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.77,0:03:07.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还说自己是什么武士
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.77,0:03:11.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近确实有人反映这类情况
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.63,0:03:14.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说是一到晚上就有个穿着全身紧身衣的男人到处乱晃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.28,0:03:17.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还自称是「正义的伙伴」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.70,0:03:18.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫什么来着…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.60,0:03:20.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后藤
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.40,0:03:23.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是叫「弗拉明戈武士」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.94,0:03:27.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这个 好吓人啊 快抓住他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.02,0:03:30.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 他也没做什么坏事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.82,0:03:33.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之 丢垃圾请按时间来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.72,0:03:36.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶诶？一般都会那样丢的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.75,0:03:43.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一般来说确实都会这样丢呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.28,0:03:54.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后藤先生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.78,0:03:57.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你吃过饭了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.93,0:04:00.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正打算去买
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.53,0:04:01.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么到我家一起吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.36,0:04:03.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有咖喱哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.80,0:04:05.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你家也就只有咖喱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.93,0:04:12.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这挂件真可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.88,0:04:14.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是我的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.71,0:04:17.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随便拿别人的东西可不好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.56,0:04:18.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎么会做那种事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.14,0:04:22.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 难道是你女朋友的？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.69,0:04:26.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一般都不会扔的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.53,0:04:28.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是晚上扔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.83,0:04:30.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猫和乌鸦会把垃圾吃得到处都是的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.33,0:04:32.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用网罩住不就好了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.55,0:04:36.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后藤先生你压根不懂饥饿的猫和乌鸦有多么凶猛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.08,0:04:38.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它们是野兽 是畜生
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.37,0:04:40.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是一样的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.19,0:04:46.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之 我们已经陆续收到了当地居民的投诉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.99,0:04:48.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正义活动也要适可而止
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.90,0:04:53.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你朋友？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.06,0:04:54.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.35,0:04:57.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我并没有朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.18,0:04:59.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了后藤先生以外
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.79,0:05:03.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别补充说明了 真恶心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.28,0:05:07.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石原小姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.23,0:05:09.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 突然造访
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.83,0:05:12.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有些资料我忘了给你 所以就带来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.62,0:05:13.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 好的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.24,0:05:14.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.30,0:05:17.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是石原小姐 我的经纪人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.27,0:05:21.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.42,0:05:24.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石原小姐很讨厌这种兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.29,0:05:26.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被她发现的话我就死定了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.39,0:05:28.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就在门口打发她走呗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.40,0:05:33.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不能赶她走 因为这里的租金基本上都是公司出的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.81,0:05:35.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛 是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.00,0:05:37.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我也有出一部分
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.19,0:05:40.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我打算争取有一天全部自己承担
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.74,0:05:41.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是现在…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.26,0:05:44.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快帮忙！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.73,0:05:45.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 好…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.46,0:05:49.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 来了！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.27,0:05:53.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 突然造访
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.60,0:05:54.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.24,0:05:59.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.63,0:06:01.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 是我的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.24,0:06:02.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.45,0:06:05.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只在你搬进这里的时候来过一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.73,0:06:06.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没搞得乱七八糟的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.03,0:06:07.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.45,0:06:09.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 你好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.96,0:06:12.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.49,0:06:16.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是羽佐间的经纪人 名叫石原
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.10,0:06:17.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫后藤
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.29,0:06:20.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后藤先生是位警察
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.82,0:06:22.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶 警察？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.57,0:06:23.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.86,0:06:24.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恕我冒昧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.14,0:06:26.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问你和羽佐间是在哪认识的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.97,0:06:31.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃 因为我也住在这一带
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.08,0:06:32.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.07,0:06:36.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 我先告辞了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.91,0:06:37.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟打扰你们就不太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.09,0:06:40.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.95,0:06:42.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.64,0:06:50.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她确实很有魄力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.28,0:06:51.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.33,0:06:54.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生起气来真的很可怕的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.25,0:06:55.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.03,0:06:56.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你的咖喱
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.59,0:06:58.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有事电话联系
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.08,0:07:03.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先 把麦克递给主唱麻里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.67,0:07:04.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.61,0:07:05.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.70,0:07:08.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,间奏的时候你还要再出场一次
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.37,0:07:09.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微跳两下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.46,0:07:10.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跳舞吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.63,0:07:11.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.50,0:07:12.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就跳一会儿
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.07,0:07:14.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会跳舞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.64,0:07:16.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那部分能不能找个替身来…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.17,0:07:18.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别自以为是了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.86,0:07:23.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以为工作人员花了多少工夫才拿下这份工作
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.44,0:07:26.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在的你只不过是个满大街都是的普通帅哥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.98,0:07:31.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后好不容易才有了一丁丁点名气
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.84,0:07:35.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今后是成为大牌还是被人像滞销商品一样叫卖
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.16,0:07:37.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就看你现在 看你现在怎么表现了啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.69,0:07:42.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你应该知道你现在的待遇很优厚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.51,0:07:44.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这说明公司对你非常看好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.81,0:07:46.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可别辜负我们的期待
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.80,0:07:47.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知 知道了…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.13,0:07:49.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.03,0:07:53.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我们从头再过一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.69,0:08:02.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你做什么呢 快过来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.25,0:08:06.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉和杂志的拍摄完全不同啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.48,0:08:08.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我紧张起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.01,0:08:12.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用紧张也没事 因为今天的主角是MMM
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.99,0:08:14.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不过就是个群众演员
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.46,0:08:16.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.61,0:08:20.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便如此 你也要争取给观众留下一点印象
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.60,0:08:22.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.91,0:08:28.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mineral Miracle Muses 入场
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.88,0:08:30.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.37,0:08:32.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好 早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.07,0:08:34.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.25,0:08:36.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.25,0:08:40.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请多关照 请多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.55,0:08:41.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你当这是选举拉票啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.77,0:08:46.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天就请多多关照了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.68,0:08:47.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.16,0:08:49.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敝人不不不才请多多包涵！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.81,0:08:51.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.12,0:08:54.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.60,0:08:55.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那小哥是咋回事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.88,0:08:59.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是树工作室的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.76,0:09:00.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.43,0:09:03.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我的名片
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.36,0:09:04.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.52,0:09:08.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是经营新闻网站「HIGH ROLLERS HI!」的今野
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.80,0:09:11.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是Caesar Pro的石原 初次见面
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.07,0:09:14.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是Caesar的人啊 今天是为何到场呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.86,0:09:16.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是来陪同我司艺人羽佐间的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.19,0:09:18.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.57,0:09:20.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是个英俊小伙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.22,0:09:22.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多谢夸奖
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.39,0:09:24.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石原小姐也很漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.12,0:09:29.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羽佐间先生走到舞台中央打开盒子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.41,0:09:30.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后麻里拿起麦克风
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.36,0:09:33.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一段我们来排练一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.47,0:09:33.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.80,0:09:34.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.97,0:09:36.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羽佐间先生 你太僵硬了点
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.85,0:09:38.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这只是彩排 所以放轻松点 好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.53,0:09:40.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes sir！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.75,0:09:42.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羽佐间先生 放松
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.50,0:09:48.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今野先生 你不用到树工作室那边看看吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.82,0:09:52.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不必担心 我已经和他们约好拍摄结束后进行采访了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.80,0:09:55.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石原小姐稍后有什么打算吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.95,0:10:02.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷静下来 羽佐间正义
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.38,0:10:06.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种程度的危机 英雄应该能轻易克服
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.52,0:10:08.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始彩排
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.44,0:10:10.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,英雄应该能…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.81,0:10:12.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 如果是红斧战士就一定没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.92,0:10:13.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 开始
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.29,0:10:21.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\i1}击碎世间的一切邪恶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.35,0:10:22.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羽佐间先生 走出来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.05,0:10:25.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\i1}用尽全力将它劈成两半
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.79,0:10:32.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\i1}将谎言筑起的罪恶都市
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.55,0:10:36.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\i1}一刀两断 正义的证明
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.15,0:10:40.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\i1}百发百中
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.71,0:10:40.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羽佐间先生 打开盒子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.28,0:10:44.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 麻里 拿起它
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.58,0:10:48.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\i1}鲜红的巨斧雄伟矗立
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.95,0:10:52.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\i1}用巨斧斩尽邪恶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.43,0:10:55.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\i1}用巨斧劈开黑夜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.73,0:10:54.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羽佐间先生 关上盒子 退场
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.70,0:10:56.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻里 戴上麦克风唱歌
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.15,0:10:58.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\i1}Kill and break! Kill and break!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.34,0:11:04.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\i1}其名曰 红斧战士
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.14,0:11:08.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你刚刚…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.24,0:11:11.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停 停！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.01,0:11:15.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 麻里？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.64,0:11:18.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.29,0:11:20.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.31,0:11:23.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重头来一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.11,0:11:26.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(part-b)
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.86,0:11:39.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.13,0:12:01.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他突然冲出来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.61,0:12:02.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趴在了地上
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.11,0:12:05.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要偷看我的内裤！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.57,0:12:10.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近 关于那个紧身衣男的举报多起来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.35,0:12:11.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他绝对是个变态
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.14,0:12:14.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快想点办法处理他啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.15,0:12:15.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.92,0:12:26.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.07,0:12:28.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 我和别人约在这儿…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.51,0:12:30.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.90,0:12:33.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你淋湿了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.92,0:12:35.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我是骑自行车来的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.57,0:12:36.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下着雨还骑车？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.10,0:12:38.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不打伞的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.40,0:12:40.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是怪人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.08,0:12:42.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是骑自行车也很不错的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.34,0:12:44.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我很快就熟悉了这一带
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.10,0:12:45.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.99,0:12:47.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请用
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.09,0:12:48.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.68,0:12:51.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,决定好要喝什么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.36,0:12:53.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请给我乌龙茶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.76,0:12:55.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么 你不喝酒吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.19,0:12:55.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.99,0:12:57.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才19岁
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.90,0:12:59.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.12,0:13:05.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暂时别再扮弗拉明戈武士了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.44,0:13:08.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？ 这么突然
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.50,0:13:12.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都说过了吧 有人来投诉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.95,0:13:15.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说是晚上有穿着紧身衣的变态出没
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.18,0:13:17.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是正义的伙伴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.72,0:13:19.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这点别人没理解啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.21,0:13:22.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你前天也被人错当成变态了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.39,0:13:25.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个是悲伤的误会
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.40,0:13:27.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光是误会解决不了问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.20,0:13:29.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您叫我吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.41,0:13:30.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再来一杯生啤
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.80,0:13:31.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.18,0:13:32.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之 别再扮弗拉明戈了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.25,0:13:36.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否则我真的会抓你了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.54,0:13:38.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚刚的台词 很有特摄片的风格呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.48,0:13:41.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 我可不是开玩笑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.16,0:13:44.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我扮英雄也是认真的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.35,0:13:46.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.39,0:13:52.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就直说了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.77,0:13:54.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你并不是在和邪恶战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.10,0:13:56.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是在制造麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.71,0:14:00.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也知道乱丢东西 提前扔垃圾这种事不好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.28,0:14:03.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我不会一一去治理 因为这种事太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.25,0:14:06.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事是不会根绝的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.38,0:14:09.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警察说这话合适吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.36,0:14:11.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,合适啊 因为我正视现实
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.01,0:14:13.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是 如果只是要提醒别人注意
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.91,0:14:15.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用你的本来面目不就行了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.40,0:14:17.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒙着个脸 不觉得很狡猾吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.49,0:14:20.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么做是因为考虑到今后的发展
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.06,0:14:22.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今后什么发展？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.26,0:14:26.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,碰上罪犯 黑社会或者邪恶军团的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.30,0:14:30.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是暴露身份就麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.74,0:14:33.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那才是我们警察的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.96,0:14:37.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一点权力都没有的你来插手反而更麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.45,0:14:40.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说到底 你凭什么指责别人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.92,0:14:43.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道你就一件亏心事都没做过？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.62,0:14:50.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是伞
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.91,0:14:51.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.40,0:14:54.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不打伞的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.43,0:14:55.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚刚听说过了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.55,0:14:56.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.28,0:14:59.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小学一年级的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.70,0:15:04.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一个雨天 我打算回家的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.37,0:15:07.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却发现我的伞不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.01,0:15:12.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我实在没辙 就打着别人的伞回家了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.65,0:15:14.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事很普遍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.82,0:15:19.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二天 班上的内田同学请假了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.93,0:15:22.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为淋着雨回家而感冒了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.59,0:15:28.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和爷爷一起去道歉 看到病倒的内田同学的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.33,0:15:32.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我意识到自己做的事就是犯罪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.02,0:15:36.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伞是日本被盗数量最多的物品
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.60,0:15:40.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为突然降雨而将别人的伞「借走」的人不在少数
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.05,0:15:45.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而被偷走伞的人又会擅自拿走别人的伞
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.93,0:15:48.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「不过就是把伞」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.38,0:15:51.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这种意识在制造犯罪的连锁
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.32,0:15:55.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罪恶就在人们的不知不觉间滋长！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.88,0:15:58.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你就不打伞了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.84,0:15:59.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.67,0:16:00.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也太大惊小怪了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.46,0:16:02.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.05,0:16:04.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害怕这样的过去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.62,0:16:09.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会让我在某个同样的雨天再次犯下偷伞的罪过
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.43,0:16:12.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说的我倒也明白
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.60,0:16:13.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你这论点太极端了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.11,0:16:17.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盗伞这种事已经成为社会体系的一部分了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.49,0:16:18.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然如此！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.73,0:16:21.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不就更应该一点点地去改变这个社会吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.11,0:16:26.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伞是否重要 不是应该由伞的主人来决定吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.71,0:16:29.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是500日元的塑料伞 也不应该去偷啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.40,0:16:32.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说你要做就低调点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.88,0:16:34.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没必要扮成弗拉明戈吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.56,0:16:37.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您叫我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.03,0:16:38.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苏打酒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.56,0:16:39.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乌龙茶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.98,0:16:44.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后藤先生 要打烊了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.87,0:16:45.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快起来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.95,0:16:47.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后藤先生？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.40,0:16:54.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经结完账了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.16,0:16:56.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之我们先出去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.89,0:16:59.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可真别再扮弗拉明戈了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.96,0:17:02.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个问题我们改天再聊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.28,0:17:03.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多谢惠顾
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.58,0:17:06.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伞没了！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.62,0:17:10.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是你女朋友的伞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.20,0:17:13.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 是她忘在我这的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.05,0:17:17.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后藤先生！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.68,0:17:23.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个混帐！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.75,0:17:25.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你干嘛！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.58,0:17:26.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红灯了！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.93,0:17:29.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.73,0:17:35.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把伞还给我！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.00,0:17:46.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我完全明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.10,0:17:48.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你所说的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.39,0:17:51.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.54,0:17:54.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后藤先生 请交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.16,0:17:59.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伞！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.03,0:18:10.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伞 伞
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.35,0:18:29.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.37,0:18:31.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伞 伞
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.98,0:18:40.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这人是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.19,0:18:41.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.46,0:18:46.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他不在这
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.21,0:19:02.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,改为B计划
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.56,0:19:14.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,换回路线A
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.64,0:19:20.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说垃圾要早上扔！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.92,0:19:21.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,躲开！ 躲开！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.82,0:19:29.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伞 伞 伞
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.46,0:19:40.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.59,0:19:55.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请把伞…请把伞还回来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.96,0:19:57.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伞？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.21,0:20:00.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那把伞不是你的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.10,0:20:02.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请你归还
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.22,0:20:04.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的也被人拿走了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.42,0:20:06.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是理由
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.32,0:20:09.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界上没有可以随便偷的伞
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.87,0:20:10.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把伞还给我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.42,0:20:14.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.71,0:20:17.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 我们去抓偷你伞的家伙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.60,0:20:20.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.59,0:20:23.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你要打电话让我看这段视频？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.74,0:20:25.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是觉得很有意思
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.08,0:20:28.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不觉得他的声音很像羽佐间吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.45,0:20:30.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不觉得
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.92,0:20:32.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.79,0:20:34.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还有工作 先挂了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.90,0:20:45.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\i1}好 我们去抓偷你伞的家伙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.03,0:20:47.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是点击率在一周内达到了9万次的热门视频
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.89,0:20:50.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 这位英雄叫什么名字呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.84,0:20:52.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初次登场的羽佐间先生
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.91,0:20:53.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗拉明戈武士
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.76,0:20:57.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别猜对啊
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(ED)
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.56,0:21:03.80,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ランプシェードが頭に被さり
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.82,0:21:06.70,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,私に目隠ししたって
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.13,0:21:10.12,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,シャツのボタンの穴から
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.37,0:21:13.14,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君を感じれるの
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.55,0:21:16.50,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妄想伝えてるサイチュー
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.80,0:21:19.61,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君が行くよとサイン
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.97,0:21:22.96,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,車の助手席乗れば
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.18,0:21:29.21,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,発車音 胸の音みたいにキュルルン
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.57,0:21:35.56,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,どんどんスキになっていい？君の事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.93,0:21:42.00,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,横顔だけで受け流す君は草食系？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.32,0:21:45.33,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冗談ばかりの会話も
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.56,0:21:51.76,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今はマジなloving you message
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.91,0:21:55.13,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,次は、ドコドコへ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.19,0:22:00.94,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,余裕綽々な君のリードに
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.00,0:22:04.77,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大人感じてノックダウン
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.78,0:22:10.53,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,どんどんアイしちゃっていい？君の事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.19,0:22:17.18,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赤信号でキスせがむ私 肉食系？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.56,0:22:20.59,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,このまま終われないデートタイム
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.75,0:22:26.56,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Baby love, イエスを聞かせて
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.56,0:21:03.80,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灯罩盖过头顶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.82,0:21:06.70,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遮住了我的眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.13,0:21:10.12,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从衬衫钮扣的缝隙里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.37,0:21:13.14,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感知到你的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.55,0:21:16.50,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在传递妄想之时
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.80,0:21:19.61,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你作出启程的示意
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.97,0:21:22.96,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乘上副驾驶座
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.18,0:21:29.21,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只听引擎声如心跳怦怦作响
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.57,0:21:35.56,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是否能越来越为你倾倒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.93,0:21:42.00,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只凭侧脸悄然回避的你难道是草食系？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.32,0:21:45.33,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不着边际的玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.56,0:21:51.76,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如今俨然已是真正的情话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.91,0:21:55.13,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你从容制定计划
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.19,0:22:00.94,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将我步步引导
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.00,0:22:04.77,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,周身散发的成熟将我攻陷
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.78,0:22:10.53,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是否能越来越爱你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.19,0:22:17.18,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁红灯之机索吻的我难道是肉食系？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.56,0:22:20.59,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永不终结的约会时光
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.75,0:22:26.56,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Baby love, 让我听到肯定的回答
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(epilogue)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.57,0:22:33.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到你知道啊 羽佐间先生
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.44,0:22:35.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为那9万次里有206次是我贡献的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.00,0:22:37.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.43,0:22:38.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么会看那么多遍呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.77,0:22:40.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃 这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.90,0:22:43.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红斧——战士！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.92,0:22:45.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是下意识地点了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.54,0:22:45.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\bord2\shad3\4a&H00&\fs44\i1\pos(592,110)\4c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H7ABEE4&\c&H4F5D5D&}惊叹 英雄在夜晚的街道上现身！？
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(next title)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.05,0:22:50.05,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真假弗拉明戈對決
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.59,0:22:54.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,后藤先生为什么会想当巡警呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.26,0:22:57.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是有部讲葛饰区的巡警的漫画吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.26,0:22:57.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fs36}注：捏他「这里是葛饰区龟有公园前派出所」 少年JUMP的最长连载作品
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.48,0:22:58.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.65,0:23:00.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大概就是因为我小时候看了那部漫画吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.04,0:23:02.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那部漫画那么早就有了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.05,0:23:05.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有啊 一直都有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.53,0:23:06.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看了之后就觉得
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.77,0:23:09.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,巡警可以佩枪
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.66,0:23:14.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还可以上班拼模型看漫画 所以很向往
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.68,0:23:17.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,后藤先生 那是漫画里才会有的设定
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.95,0:23:18.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.01,0:23:20.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是说你有资格说这话吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.25,0:23:21.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有你绝对没资格说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.50,0:23:25.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在想来 那个人大概就是我的英雄吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.11,0:23:29.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现实地想 那个人已经超越了完美的范畴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.42,0:23:34.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,了不起啊…喂 为什么这一点上偏偏现实起来了！
